// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2835 — Mass File Rename (cloak)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ef81aedc-9d18-5526-b038-6c9f51149227

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
